# Changelog

All notable changes to this skill will be documented in this file.

## [1.0.0] - 2025-12-27

### Initial Creation

**RED Phase Documentation:**
- Gap: Claude/agents don't know @praetorian-chariot/ui is being decommissioned
- Failure: Agents import from deprecated library instead of local components
- Failure: Agents don't know migration workflow (recursive dependencies, reference updates)

**Skill Type:** Process/Pattern
**Category:** development/frontend
**Location:** Library (.claude/skill-library/)

### Added
- Component source selection decision tree
- 4-phase migration workflow (discover, migrate, update refs, verify)
- Import transformation rules
- Target directory mapping
- User interaction prompts for migration decisions
- Edge case handling (existing local, circular deps, type exports)
- Reference files:
  - `references/import-transforms.md` - Detailed import rules
  - `references/migration-example.md` - Full Tag component walkthrough
